<[[https://turbonomic.com/resources/choosing-between-aws-and-azure-webinar/]]> This is your last chance to register for tomorrow's webinar: Choosing Between AWS and Azure - How Turbonomic Enables a Data-Driven Decision.
<[[https://turbonomic.com/resources/choosing-between-aws-and-azure-webinar/]]>
Our Cloud Migration planning enables intelligent, data-backed analysis of which cloud (or clouds) fits best based on your requirements. The webinar will be live on Thursday, April 26th at 11 AM ET <[[https://turbonomic.com/resources/choosing-between-aws-and-azure-webinar]]>.
Can't make it at that time? Register now, and we'll send you the recording afterwards.
Regards, Team Turbonomic
